18:09.248 --> 18:11.483
♪ Everybody kiss my butt ♪
♪ Kiss her butt ♪

18:11.484 --> 18:13.585
♪ Everybody kiss my butt ♪
♪ Everybody kiss her butt ♪

18:13.586 --> 18:15.754
♪ Everybody kiss my butt ♪
♪ Everybody kiss her butt ♪

18:15.755 --> 18:16.988
Yeah!

18:19.325 --> 18:21.393
Teddy!
Bob.

18:21.394 --> 18:23.395
You didn't order the Belt Buckle
Belly Buster, did you?

18:23.396 --> 18:25.397
Maybe I did,
maybe I didn't.

18:25.398 --> 18:27.899
But I did. Excuse me.
Uh, are you Dusty?

18:27.900 --> 18:30.569
Dusty?
Uh, no. There's no Dusty.

18:30.570 --> 18:33.905
Uh, this is a chain, pal.
I'm Kevin. I'm the manager.

18:33.906 --> 18:36.608
Listen, Kevin, you can't serve
this guy your five-pound burger.

18:36.609 --> 18:38.343
Oh, okay, making a note.

18:38.344 --> 18:40.645
I can't serve someone a burger
in my own restaurant.

18:40.680 --> 18:42.113
Look, Teddy is... Well...

18:42.114 --> 18:44.316
He has the biggest heart
of anyone I know.

18:44.350 --> 18:45.817
Both because
he's incredibly sweet

18:45.818 --> 18:47.319
but also
because it's full

18:47.353 --> 18:49.521
of cholesterol.
Which is why you can't serve him

18:49.522 --> 18:52.124
that huge burger...
he-he might not survive it.

18:52.158 --> 18:53.825
Well, you know what?
Big boy paid for it,

18:53.826 --> 18:55.127
so order up!

18:55.128 --> 18:56.862
Good God,
look at that thing. Oh.

18:56.863 --> 18:59.030
Let me at it!
You're not giving him that burger.

18:59.031 --> 19:01.700
Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey. Come on,
let that Belly Buster through.

19:01.701 --> 19:03.969
Please take the burger back to
the kitchen, ma'am.

19:03.970 --> 19:07.372
It is so weird that you think
you work here. I just...

19:07.373 --> 19:09.808
Damn it, I don't remember
hiring a fat Burt Reynolds.

19:09.809 --> 19:11.977
Look, this burger
is not going anywhere.

19:11.978 --> 19:13.812
This is just
fantastic.

19:13.846 --> 19:16.481
I'm gonna get to throw fat Burt
Reynolds out of my restaurant!

19:16.516 --> 19:18.483
Oh, yeah?
Well, I can get tough, too.

19:18.518 --> 19:20.852
And I'm staying. Guys, come on.
Don't fight over me.

19:20.853 --> 19:22.487
Wait, is that what's happening?

19:22.522 --> 19:24.790
Bad news for you, Kevin.
I've just been through

19:24.791 --> 19:26.792
a bunch of kick-ass training,
so if you think

19:26.793 --> 19:28.627
you can just...
Oh, no...

19:28.628 --> 19:31.463
Oh, yeah? Well, I hope you got
trained to get your ass kicked!

19:31.464 --> 19:33.198
Actually, I did! Oh, God!

19:33.199 --> 19:35.300
Here comes the glass!

19:36.202 --> 19:38.970
Thanks for coming!

19:38.971 --> 19:40.505
Are you okay, Bobby?

19:40.540 --> 19:42.340
Real glass hurts so bad.

19:42.341 --> 19:43.542
Am I bleeding?

19:43.576 --> 19:45.143
Not, like, too much.

19:45.144 --> 19:46.545
And the concrete wasn't padded.

19:46.546 --> 19:48.880
It was so hard
when-when I landed on it.

19:48.915 --> 19:51.683
Before you pass out, that's the nicest
thing anyone's ever done for me.

19:51.684 --> 19:54.386
I have so much glass in myself.
I'll get you out of here, buddy.

19:54.420 --> 19:55.687
All right, let's go
to the hospital, Teddy.

19:55.688 --> 19:57.556
No, Bob. Let's go home.

19:57.557 --> 19:59.558
No. No, we're gonna go to
a hospital... Shh, shh, shh.

19:59.559 --> 20:01.526
Home it is, Bob.

20:01.527 --> 20:03.562
Here we go, almost home.

20:03.563 --> 20:06.064
I'll just see if
someone else can take me.

20:06.099 --> 20:07.699
Hey, even though
I'm not your best friend,

20:07.700 --> 20:09.434
I really appreciate
what you did.

20:09.435 --> 20:11.870
Look, I-I'm sorry I said
you're not my best friend.

20:11.871 --> 20:13.872
Because you are.
I am?

20:13.873 --> 20:16.108
Yeah, I mean, it depends
on how you define it.

20:16.109 --> 20:18.610
You technically
are my best friend.

20:18.611 --> 20:20.946
But, I mean... I might meet... Bup,
bup, bup... stop right there, Bobby.

20:20.947 --> 20:22.948
But, I mean, I don't know who...
Yeah. Bob, Bob, Bob, Bob.

20:22.949 --> 20:25.550
Eventually I... Enough.
Can I carry you across the threshold?

20:25.551 --> 20:26.918
All right.

20:28.955 --> 20:31.323
Ow.
Watch your head. Sorry.

20:31.357 --> 20:33.859
Aw, my little beat-up Bobby.

20:33.860 --> 20:35.694
Where's that belt from?
Where's all the food?

20:35.695 --> 20:37.696
Shh, shh, shh, shh, shush.
Is the ice helping?

20:37.697 --> 20:40.032
Pretty refreshing, right?
Yes, Tina.

20:40.033 --> 20:41.600
How 'bout this?
Is this helping?

20:41.601 --> 20:43.368
Thanks, Teddy.
Yes, it's good.

20:43.369 --> 20:46.371
How 'bout some smelling salts?
Oh, God. Come on!

20:46.372 --> 20:47.957
Oh, you come on.

20:47.958 --> 20:49.999
That fart's a winner
and you know it!

20:50.000 --> 20:51.504
All right,
let me smell it again.

20:51.505 --> 20:53.879
Yeah, you're right.

